OL,3,CMan arrested by counter-terror police
OL,4,Cover attacks on Jewish sites in London
OL,6,FA 37-year-old man has been arrested by
OL,7,Fcounter-terror police investigating a
OL,8,Fstring of attacks on Jewish sites in
OL,9,FLondon.
OL,11,FThe man was arrested at an address
OL,12,Fnear Barnstaple, Devon, on Sunday, on
OL,13,Fsuspicion of preparing terrorist acts,
OL,14,Fthe Metropolitan Police said.
OL,16,FThe force said 26 people have been
OL,17,Farrested over the series of attacks on
OL,18,FJewish sites since late March.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/4
