PN,31902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1777327868
OL,3,CMan arrested by counter-terror police
OL,4,Cover attacks on Jewish sites in London
OL,6,FEight people have been charged with
OL,7,Farson-related offences, and one person
OL,8,Fhas been convicted of arson.
OL,10,FThere have been arson attacks on
OL,11,FJewish community ambulances in Golders
OL,12,FGreen, north-west London, a synagogue
OL,13,Fand a former Jewish charity, as well
OL,14,Fas an incident where a drone was flown
OL,15,Fnear the Israeli embassy.
OL,17,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,18,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,19,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,20,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/4
