PN,31903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1777327868
OL,3,CMan arrested by counter-terror police
OL,4,Cover attacks on Jewish sites in London
OL,6,FCounter-terror police have been
OL,7,Flooking into the possible involvement
OL,8,Fof Iranian proxies.
OL,10,FPremises linked to people opposing the
OL,11,FIranian regime have also been
OL,12,Ftargeted, the Met said last week.
OL,14,FAn attempted arson attack was also
OL,15,Fcarried out at Finchley Reform
OL,16,FSynagogue on April 15 outside the
OL,17,Foffices of a Persian media company,
OL,18,Fboth in north-west London.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/4
